🎯 Project Overview

This project is a Stock Forecasting and Trading Simulation system built using TensorFlow.js.
It allows users to:

Train an LSTM model directly in the browser
Predict stock prices
Simulate buy/sell decisions
🧰 Technologies Used
ECharts & D3.js → Data visualization
PapaParse → CSV file parsing
TensorFlow.js → Machine learning (LSTM model)
NumJS & Numeric.js → Numerical computations
⚙️ How It Works
Step 1: Run the Project
Open index.html in a browser
👉 No installation required
Step 2: Configure Parameters
Set hyperparameters like:
Learning rate
Epochs
LSTM size
Future prediction days
Step 3: Upload Dataset
Upload stock CSV (e.g., from Yahoo Finance)
Step 4: Train Model
Click Train
Model learns patterns from historical data
Step 5: Results

After training, system shows:

📈 Stock prediction graph
📊 Loss graph
📉 Distribution comparison
💰 Buy/Sell simulation
🚀 Key Features
Runs fully in browser (no backend required)
Real-time training and prediction
Interactive charts and visualizations
Trading strategy simulation
⚠️ Important Note
This is for educational purposes only
Not suitable for real stock trading
